I caught the capital R eventually.

@dutchiris

I didn't know CHILE either, but it became apparent with a few crosses and made sense geographically. One more factoid learned from a xword puzzle! 

GRACE HOPPER filled in from the crosses too.  Didn't know that one either. Luckily, I was going from the bottom up, so I already had enough filled in to know it wasn't Ada Lovelace.

@Justin

